    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A majestic train rolls in from the impossible, roiling fog. A charismatic train conductor steps out and welcomes you on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are the other passengers just some eccentric rich people, or could there be something more? And why do you get the feeling that the conductor is hiding something? <br><br>There's only one way to find out. All aboard...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/5683b834b8c12791234e298f577dec75.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/5683b834b8c12791234e298f577dec75.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=96 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Are you ready to uncover their secrets?</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Vivienne Sanssouci, a daring journalist who has been tasked with reviewing the Ouroboros Express.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But this is no mere luxury liner, and a devastating secret soon upends her life and those of the other passengers...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/7cd9e8ac56b054918d696b5319f5a14a.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/7cd9e8ac56b054918d696b5319f5a14a.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice-acted</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Diverse Love Interests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of content at 50,000+ words</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Stats-Raising Systems (Attraction &amp; Cosmic Decay)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/fcac765ec1fb20b8c6f29962fc2a25e1.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/fcac765ec1fb20b8c6f29962fc2a25e1.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/16aa9fd6088450042ae87a695433cca3.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/16aa9fd6088450042ae87a695433cca3.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=578 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/3504bc8e11b6fe14a1a720b551389c89.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/3504bc8e11b6fe14a1a720b551389c89.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=578 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/74165023056eeaf4b8f2ed3cfa55443a.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/74165023056eeaf4b8f2ed3cfa55443a.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=578 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras/5348f58bcc39ab91bd90a338d48ba5bf.avif?t=1745675508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234430/extras_big/5348f58bcc39ab91bd90a338d48ba5bf.avif?t=1745675508 width=800 height=578 /></span><spa